data.description: Beautifully updated home in Oak Valley Estates. This 4-2 +office sits on a gorgeous lot with fantastic curb appeal and mature trees. Inside the home, you will find amenities such as hardwood floors, crown molding, decorative lighting, and much more. Enjoy a great entertainment flow with this fantastic open layout. Kitchen is complete with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar. Get cozy in the large living area next to the stone fireplace. Master bedroom boasts an ensuite with dual sinks, a garden tub, a separate shower, and a walk-in closet. Head to the backyard and find your own personal oasis. Covered patio overlooks pool with tanning deck & waterfall features! DON'T MISS OUT!!
